snippet.title: I Wanna Be The SuperTux Part 1/2
snippet.description:
Find my SuperTux levels in https://miksy91productions.herokuapp.com/

This is a big level which I've created for SuperTux 0.3.1 version. It's quite difficult, and name comes from IWBTG (IWBTST)
Make sure you won't die because if you do you need to start from beginning again :P
